'''卡马利亚斯龙属'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Camarillasaurus''}}，意为“{{link-en|卡马利亚斯组|Camarillas Formation}}的蜥蜴”）是一[[属|属]][[兽脚类|兽脚类]][[恐龙|恐龙]]，生存於[[白垩纪|白垩纪]][[期_(地质学)|早期]]（[[巴列姆阶|巴列姆阶]]）西班牙南部[[特鲁埃尔省|特鲁埃尔省]]的[[卡马里利亚斯|卡马里利亚斯]]。根据一份2019年的论文中得出的结论，它很有可能是一种[[棘龙科|棘龙科]]；但在2014年最初描述它的论文中，它被认为是一种[[角鼻龙类|角鼻龙类]]。<ref name=Camarillasaurus/>

==叙述==
[[File:Camarillasaurus_cirugedae.jpg|upright]]与骶骨椎体]]
该属的[[化石|化石]]发现于{{link-en|卡马利亚斯组|Camarillas Formation}}，[[模式种|模式种]]是'''西氏卡马利亚斯龙'''（''Camarillasaurus cirugedae''），由[[古生物学家|古生物学家]]Bárbara Sánchez-Hernández与{{link-en|迈克尔·本顿|Michael Benton}}等人在2014年叙述。叙述者们认为它是一种基础[[角鼻龙类|角鼻龙类]]，考虑到模式标本死亡时的年龄，它的骨骼结构有些不寻常。<ref name=Camarillasaurus>{{Cite journal | last1 = Sánchez-Hernández | first1 = B. R. | last2 = Benton | first2 = M. | title = Filling the ceratosaur gap: A new ceratosaurian theropod from the Early Cretaceous of Spain | url = http://www.app.pan.pl/article/item/app20110144.html | doi = 10.4202/app.2011.0144 | journal = Acta Palaeontologica Polonica | year = 2014 | volume = 59 | issue = 3 | pages = 581–600 | pmid =  | pmc =  | doi-access =  | access-date = 2020-07-19 | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127182725/http://www.app.pan.pl/article/item/app20110144.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>但是在EAVP2019年正式会议上给出的摘要中，奥利弗·劳赫（Oliver Rauhut）及其同事根据模式标本[[椎骨|尾椎]]的特征以及化石发现地最新找到的材料而建议将其作为[[棘龙科|棘龙科]]成员，而不是[[角鼻龙科|角鼻龙科]]。<ref>O. W. M. Rauhut, J. Ignacio Canudo, D. Castanera A (2019) [https://docs.wixstatic.com/ugd/4abdcf_6d667de7460e4a489c8a49a9760414b9.pdf?index=true A REAPPRAISAL OF THE EARLY CRETACEOUS THEROPOD DINOSAUR CAMARILLASAURUS FROM SPAIN] {{Wayback|url=https://docs.wixstatic.com/ugd/4abdcf_6d667de7460e4a489c8a49a9760414b9.pdf?index=true |date=20200613005339 }} ''XVII Conference of the EAVP – Brussels, Belgium''</ref>Adun Samathi在2019年发表的论文中得出了同样的结论。<ref>Adun Samathi (2019) CHAPTER 6: "A Spinosaurid from Thailand and the Reassessment of ''Camarillasaurus'' from the Early Cretaceous of Spain" in [http://hss.ulb.uni-bonn.de/2019/5605/5605.pdf THEROPOD DINOSAURS FROM THAILAND AND SOUTHEAST ASIA PHYLOGENY, EVOLUTION, AND PALEOBIOGEOGRAPHY] {{Wayback|url=http://hss.ulb.uni-bonn.de/2019/5605/5605.pdf |date=20201103193405 }} Dissertation Thesis, University of Bonn pp.161-181</ref>

